```python
import pandas as pd

df_tx = pd.DataFrame({
    "cust_id": ["C1","C1","C1","C2","C2","C3","C3","C3"],
    "date": pd.to_datetime([
        "2024-01-01","2024-01-05","2024-01-10",
        "2024-01-03","2024-01-20",
        "2024-01-02","2024-01-15","2024-01-25"
    ]),
    "amount": [100,150,200,80,120,50,60,300]
})

df_segment = pd.DataFrame({
    "cust_id": ["C1","C1","C2","C3","C3"],
    "start_dt": pd.to_datetime([
        "2023-12-01","2024-01-07",
        "2024-01-01",
        "2023-12-01","2024-01-20"
    ]),
    "end_dt": pd.to_datetime([
        "2024-01-06","2024-02-01",
        "2024-02-01",
        "2024-01-19","2024-02-28"
    ]),
    "segment": ["A","B","A","C","VIP"]
})
display(df_tx, df_segment)
```

# ÌíÄÏù¥

```python
tmp = df_tx.merge(df_segment, on='cust_id', how='left')
tmp = tmp[(tmp['start_dt']<=tmp['date']) & (tmp['date']<=tmp['end_dt'])]

# Í∞ôÏùÄ Í±∞Îûò(cust_id, date)Ïóê ÎåÄÌï¥ start_dtÍ∞Ä Í∞ÄÏû• ÌÅ∞(Í∞ÄÏû• ÏµúÍ∑º) segment ÏÑ†ÌÉù
df_merged = (tmp.sort_values(['cust_id','date','start_dt'], ascending=[True,True,False])
               .drop_duplicates(subset=['cust_id','date'], keep='first')
               .reset_index(drop=True))
display(df_merged)
segment_feat = df_merged.groupby('segment').agg(
    tx_cnt = ('date', 'size'),
    total_amount = ('amount', 'sum'),
    avg_amount = ('amount', 'mean'),
).reset_index().sort_values(by= 'total_amount', ascending=False)
display(segment_feat)
df_merged['is_vip'] = df_merged['segment']=='VIP'
display(df_merged)
```

```python
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
fig1, ax1 = plt.subplots(figsize=(7,4))
ax1.bar(segment_feat['segment'], segment_feat['total_amount'])
ax1.set_title("Total Amount by Segment")
ax1.grid(False)
fig2, ax2 = plt.subplots(figsize=(7,4))
custs = ['C1','C2','C3']
for idx, cust in enumerate(custs):
    r = df_merged[df_merged['cust_id']==cust].sort_values('date')
    r_scatter = df_merged[(df_merged['cust_id']==cust) &(df_merged['is_vip'])]
    ax2.plot(r['date'], r['amount'])
    ax2.scatter(r_scatter['date'], r_scatter['amount'], color= 'red')
ax2.grid(False)
```
